{"id":311139,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/08/西坡-鉴屎记：评新华社批薛蛮子奇文/","date":"2013-08-29T04:38:04Z","modified":"2013-09-20T09:27:53Z","title":"西坡 | 鉴屎记：评新华社批薛蛮子奇文","content":"<p>@西坡：《鉴屎记》：有一些文章是不配引起驳斥甚至骂声的，近来尤多，最近者如昨晚新华社发的<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/08/%e3%80%90%e5%bc%82%e9%97%bb%e8%a7%82%e6%ad%a2%e3%80%91%e6%96%b0%e5%8d%8e%e7%bd%91-%e8%96%9b%e8%9b%ae%e5%ad%90%e5%ab%96%e5%a8%bc%e8%a2%ab%e6%8b%98%ef%bc%9a%e4%bc%aa%e5%96%84%e9%9d%a2%e5%85%b7/\" target=\"_blank\">《薛蛮子跌下道德神坛的警示》</a>。就像马路上，任谁都能一眼看出前面那坨是屎，但真要扒拉开那黑黄之物，鉴出质地、品出等级，需要非常的道德勇气。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/49648916jw1e83dealduhj20c81jhajh.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-311141\" alt=\"49648916jw1e83dealduhj20c81jhajh\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/49648916jw1e83dealduhj20c81jhajh.jpg\" width=\"440\" height=\"1997\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/49648916jw1e83dealduhj20c81jhajh.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/49648916jw1e83dealduhj20c81jhajh-66x300.jpg 66w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18270,18269,9203,10466],"tags":[10216,14238,8620,23674]}